ame="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8629">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8636">본인인증</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8644">NICE평가정보</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8656">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8663">결제 시 개인신용정보 조회</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8681">코스콤</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8688">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8695">통합 회원제(L.POINT) 운영 업무</p></td><td rowspan="3" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8720">롯데멤버스㈜</p></td><td rowspan="3" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8730">㈜메타엠, 롯데정보통신㈜,<br>SCI평가정보㈜, ㈜한국모바일인증</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8769">주문 상품의 결제 대행</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8787">L.POINT 이용 내역 관리/운영 업무</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8815">통합 메시징 서비스</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8829">㈜롯데정보통신, 비즈톡</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8845">㈜카카오, ㈜KT, ㈜엘지유플러스, ㈜다우기술</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8876">이벤트 및 행사 운영 업무</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8894">대행사 선정 시 업데이트 </p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8912">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8918">고객 상담 내역 분석</p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8933">대행사 선정 시 업데이트 </p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8951">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8957">주문상품의 결제 대행</p></td><td rowspan="2" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8972">KSNET</p></td><td rowspan="2" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="253"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8981">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="8987">판매자(셀러) 대상 환급 및 송금 서비스 대행</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="282"><p data-renderer-start-pos="9018"><em data-renderer-mark="true"><span data-renderer-mark="true" data-text-custom-color="#97a0af" class="fabric-text-color-mark" style="--custom-text-color:#97a0af;"><span data-renderer-mark="true" style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span id="b576ecb2-9664-42fd-bfe0-ec4754536979" data-renderer-mark="true" data-mark-type="annotation" data-mark-annotation-type="inlineComment" data-id="b576ecb2-9664-42fd-bfe0-ec4754536979" class="inline-highlight">롯데ON 광고 대행 영업</span></span></span></em></p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-colwidth="225"><p data-renderer-start-pos="9035"><em data-renderer-mark="true"><span data-renderer-mark="true" data-text-custom-color="#97a0af" class="fabric-text-color-mark" style="--custom-text-color:#97a0af;"><span data-renderer-mark="true" style="text-decoration: line-through;">주식회사 다윈애드컴, ㈜웰커뮤니케이션즈,&nbsp;㈜온더트리플러스</span></span></em></p></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1" colorname="" data-